title: Various Artists - Small Tribute to Trip Hop X [trip-hop]
description:
An year ago, the most comprehensive blog on trip-hop music I could have thought of, Trip Hop X, has falled down Blogspot&#039;s toilet, mostly thanks to the "friends" from Mudville. But no, they haven&#039;t bit the mud and made a graceful return on Wordpress. Well, now we should ask ourselves whether it will ever rise again. Maybe they will return some place else, but until then let&#039;s take a break and think about all those trip-hop bands you wouldn&#039;t have heard (of) if it wasn&#039;t for this great blog. Even I admit I&#039;ve made quite a few interesting, unexpected discoveries. What we got here? Over an hour of some of the best trip-hop stuff that was presented on this blog (from both Wordpress and Blogspot eras). Long live trip-hop music.
